displayChart.description: Your weekly update of the most popular tracks in Ludhiana, India.

highlights.text: Schedule by Tegi Pannu and Manni Sandhu has been on Top Songs Ludhiana the longest, at 66 weeks straight.
Moon Rise by Guru Randhawa and Sanjoy is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Ludhiana, up 23 spots at #20.
Sidhu Moose Wala has the most spots on Top Songs Ludhiana. Never Fold is the highest at #6.
Pecha by Gur Sidhu and Deepak Dhillon is the highest new entry on Top Songs Ludhiana at #45.
